      <title>时间还是金钱？大选升温之际，什么才是更好的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/should-i-donate-to-harris-or-trump-research-shows-voters-prefer-volunteering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当美国人思考如何参与总统竞选时，研究表明，他们往往更愿意做志愿者而不是捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/should-i-donate-to-harris-or-trump-research-shows-voters-prefer-volunteering</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 17:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
